<div id='sourceList' class='content archiveContent'>

welcome to the blinkies archive.

blinkies.cafe offers two types of blinkies:<br>
&nbsp;- <b>original</b>, drawn by blinkies.cafe.<br>
&nbsp;- <b>archived</b>, from elsewhere on the web.<br>
<br>

when we add a blinkie from the web, we archive a copy, then create a template version without text. these template versions are used by the <a href='/'>blinkies maker</a>.<br><br>

the archived copies live here, with links to their sources and generator pages. all blinkies not on this page are original.<br><br>

<div class='tableWrapper'>
<table id='blinkieTable'>
    <tr>
        <!--extra spaces after blinkie col head for alignment-->
